{"tid":2217090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【大結局】姊弟戀性虐案 女被告四項蓄意傷人罪成","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T12:31:07.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f64db8a50bd9a5703327fdeb52be83b46e39d2","tid":2217090,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:44:12.000Z","msg":"從未拍拖的32歲一級榮譽畢業生前年透過極速約會，結識比他年長6年的保險女經紀，姊弟戀極速進入談婚論嫁階段；惟女方涉嫌多次虐待男友，包括以風筒熱風吹男友陰莖至起水泡，及後復以剛煲滾的水淋向他的大腿，亦疑嫌棄兩人性交太快完事，狠咬男友上半身至流血，又將他撼頭埋牆甚至鉸剪插心口等。女友早前於區域法院受審，暫委法官張天雁今裁決時指，男事主誠實可靠，女被告證供不誠實，不合理，裁定女被告四罪罪成。<br />\n<br />\n女被告麥凱晴（又名麥嘉雯）否認四項蓄意傷人及一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，控罪指她於2018年5月至8月在跑馬地住所犯案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NNcPOlsuxhtLFaiYCaXNESpHv8o=/802x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55MHXDFYUZAO7PUD6BL575NRHA.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNNcPOlsuxhtLFaiYCaXNESpHv8o%3D%2F802x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55MHXDFYUZAO7PUD6BL575NRHA.jpeg&h=8f6564e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主X早前於審訊時承認，與被告有進行性虐戀（SM）的習慣，但他自言純粹因害怕被告會基於得不到性滿足而施襲，才會就範；若被告的要求不會對他或其家人造成傷害，他便會照做。他又透露，被告不想懷孕，卻又不願他使用避孕套；由於他深愛被告，故於前年應她要求而結紮，永久避孕。<br />\n<br />\n控方曾於結案陳詞中指出，男事主對女友付出無條件的愛，卻承受對方的虐待、壓迫及暴力對待，形容在整段「有毒關係」之中，男事主成了「愛的俘虜」；辯方則指，專家報告認為事主傷勢似自殘造成，控方未能證明傷勢一定由女被告造成。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCCC1193/18】"},{"pid":"0dbea3261feef03459b02199a4075e934020cac3","tid":2217090,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/EZSWLNGWS5CHNGGJQUCQDZKFYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FEZSWLNGWS5CHNGGJQUCQDZKFYU%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwznyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=42b24028\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FEZSWLNGWS5CHNGGJQUCQDZKFYU%2F&h=256775e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/EZSWLNGWS5CHNGGJQUCQDZKFYU/</a>"},{"pid":"375b98df22249ecd38e689528808eddb33e0bb3d","tid":2217090,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc78e9c71b9a6c03228fcedfcdc8220ae8f96ee","tid":2217090,"uid":111460,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"遲d蓋清會唔會上庭告yoyo？"},{"pid":"a15acbaa5a39b405e2fe3fc10c3606bb75eced60","tid":2217090,"uid":370705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:48:17.000Z","msg":"好想聽啤梨哥點講<br />\n笑死方哥二號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b5995903b75eab1f8060b0dbad8a88dd246da4","tid":2217090,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cc78e9c71b9a6c03228fcedfcdc8220ae8f96ee","tid":2217090,"uid":111460,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"遲d蓋清會唔會上庭告yoyo？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"仲漏緊屎水上唔到庭"},{"pid":"1f15d991af386e2e82337cf7841beef81bb80b0d","tid":2217090,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05b5995903b75eab1f8060b0dbad8a88dd246da4","tid":2217090,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cc78e9c71b9a6c03228fcedfcdc8220ae8f96ee","tid":2217090,"uid":111460,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"遲d蓋清會唔會上庭告yoyo？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"仲漏緊屎水上唔到庭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:31:07.000Z","msg":"包住屎片咪得"}]}